'''Wally Wingert''' (born [[May 6]], [[1960s#1961|1961]]) is an American actor who voices [[Reti]] in [[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']] and ''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]''.

{{Bio-stub}}

==Roles==
*''[[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|Star Wars: Starfighter]]'' &ndash; Reti
*''[[Star Wars: Jedi Starfighter]]'' &ndash; Reti, Nym Pilot 3
*''[[Star Wars: Bounty Hunter]]'' &ndash; [[Bendix Fust]], [[Jervis Gloom]], Male civilian #1
*''[[Kinect Star Wars]]''
*''[[Disney Infinity 3.0]]''
*''[[Star Wars: Andor]]'' &ndash; "Welcome to [[Ghorman]]" Narrator (voice, in "[[One Year Later]]")

